py_progs
a variety of useful python scripts for use with ExoCAM

sys.in 	     	    	        -- contains system information (paths)
exocampy_tools.py               -- a collection of standard tools for manipulating CAM files
changevert_cesm.py              -- change the numnber of vertical levels in CAM .i. files
broadband_albedo_calculator.py  -- script to produce SED weighted snow and ice
				   albedo for user_nl_cice
